  package_label_principal_display_panel: "PACKAGE LABEL.PRINCIPAL DISPLAY PANEL NDC 66336-0815-XX NDC 66336-0815-30 NDC 66336-0815-60 Pharmacist: Dispense the Medication Guide provided separately to each patient. NDC 66336-0815-XX",
